, and installed and; implemented QuickBooks Desktop.; CEO and Founding Partner, ABM Advisory Services, Bangladesh Jul 2019 – April 2022; ● Supervised overall business strategy, planning, and operations; ● Acquisition of Clients while maintaining communication and relationships with external stakeholders; ● Managed several projects under my firm including accounting system development, internal control system development, internal; audit, financial feasibility study, tax and VAT management; Manager, Planning, Information & Control, Advanced Chemical Industries Limited, Bangladesh May 2018 - Apr 2019; ACI Limited is one of the largest conglomerates in Bangladesh. The company operates through three reportable segments: Pharmaceuticals,; Consumer Brands, and Agribusiness.; ● Head of FP&A, led a large team of financial analysts, prepared dashboards for several reports; ● Prepared executive reports on competitive analysis for various product lines, costing, marketing, Project Management, and payroll; to facilitate decision-making of directors; ● Reformed working capital management systems, planning and implementing internal control systems; ● Synchronized master budget with the budget of the respective segment, reviewing the budget and variance analysis, taking; predominantly feed-forward control, and where applicable taking feedback control; ● Prepared cash budget, and risk-return analysis; ● Analysis of Inventory management, item-wise aging of inventory, identifying slow-moving inventory, and exploring a way to dispose; of them properly by having a constructive discussion with respecting segment head; ● Reformed Costing Methodology and made factory costing easier by analyzing Bill of Material and overall costing process and; improved Gross Profit margin by proper costing and product mix selection; ● Supervised Cost analysts and variance analysts and train them to work on cost more effectively and created SOP; Assistant Manager, Financial Analyst, BetaOne Investments Limited, Bangladesh Jun 2014 - Apr 2018; BetaOne Investments Limited is a renowned Merchant Bank in Bangladesh.; ● Dealt with millions of data and built in-house e-library of financial information of the publicly listed company and pioneered; research department in the company; ● Financial analyst for publicly listed companies and Multinational companies in Bangladesh - Stock Valuation, Cash Flow Projection,; Business Projection, Budget and Variance analysis, Long-term and Short-term financial planning; ● Risk-return analysis for various portfolio; ● Member of Investment Committee, prepared investment globe, assist in deciding investment policy, designed fee’s structure, and; participate in product designing of portfolio department; ● Prepared project proposals handled IPO and other corporate finance-related works including Business & Financial Analysis,; Financial Modelling & Feasibility Study."}]'::jsonb, 'F:\Resume All 1\Resume PDF\CV_Eliza Hossain Bristy FCCA.pdf', 'Name: Drive Growth.

